{
  "stem": "617.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they walked for a while, but nobody wanted to be the last or close to the last.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Everybody wanted to try to be at least in the middle or in the front of the procession, and-- because the SS soldiers were walking with us on both sides and in the back.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And if they saw anybody who wasn't able to, they would just take them out to the side of the road and shoot them and leave them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I'll never forget, when these three sisters were pulling their sister-- the two were pulling their sisters, and the SS noticed, they just took her out from their arms to the side of the road and shot her right in front of them, in front of everybody.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we had to go on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we were walking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And at one place, we came to a bridge.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we were asked to go fast, fast, fast across the bridge.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Not to linger on, you know, go real fast.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And as soon as we crossed the bridge, the bridge was blown up, because I guess they thought that that will keep the Russians from advancing so fast.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we kept on going for about five days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And that's when our saved bread came to very good use, because some days we didn't get anything to eat at all.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we had about 50 slices of bread saved, my sister and I.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we would eat that, and we would share it with the others who didn't have anything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because a lot of them just-- when they got their rations, they would eat it up, and that was it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was very-- came in really handy, that saving.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sometimes when we stopped at night, they would give us something.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
